code: export function slugConverter(name){return name.toLowerCase().split(' ').join('_');}export function nameConverter(name){return name.toLowerCase().split('_').map(function(word){return word.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+word.slice(1);}).join(' ');}export function capitalizeConverter(name){return name.toLowerCase().split(' ').map(function(word){return word.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+word.slice(1);}).join(' ');}
